  - Priority: MEDIUM
  - Purpose: Layers, states, directional, icon_state, overlays/underlays
  - Notes: Visual asset creation

- **Sound/Music Guide**: https://github.com/tgstation/tgstation/blob/master/docs/Sounds.md
  - Priority: LOW
  - Purpose: Formats, volume, paths, licenses
  - Notes: Audio asset guidelines

